A 40 year old man stabbed his wife eight times and turned the knife on self after a domestic quarrel in Kibera.The woman died while undergoing treatment at Kenyatta National Hospital on Thursday where the man is also admitted in critical condition.Geoffrey Shitero stabbed his wife, Jackline Asiko, 31, on Wednesday night at their home using a kitchen knife. Nairobi CID chief Ireri Kamwende said police have opened investigations into the gruesome murder.The couple is said to have reunited only two weeks ago after separating for three years.